16:T504,This is a capital equipment endoscopy camera system for sports medicine/arthroscopy applications. Internal evidence is technically detailed and coherent: Full HD Sony CMOS sensor, 1920x1080 resolution, multiple video outputs (DVI/HDMI/CVBS), integrated 80W LED light source, IPX-8 waterproof camera head, 11 surgery modes, USB storage, and video playback. The system belongs to the PERSIST product family under Sports Medicine division. However, critical ambiguities require review: (1) Brand is empty - manufacturer appears to be Meril Life Sciences but PERSIST brand ownership/licensing unclear without external verification, (2) No external sources found to validate PERSIST as established brand or this specific model, (3) Cannot verify whether this is OEM/rebranded equipment or proprietary Meril system, (4) 11 surgery modes suggest multi-specialty use beyond just sports medicine (could include general surgery, ENT, urology, etc.) but division classification limits it to Sports Medicine only. Technical specifications are complete and credible for a modern HD endoscopy system. Recommend review to: confirm brand ownership, verify manufacturer claims, clarify multi-specialty vs sports medicine positioning, and potentially source external validation for PERSIST system line.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"PERSIST FHD Endoscope Camera System\",\"description\":\"Full HD endoscope camera with 1/2.3-inch Sony CMOS sensor. 2.1M pixels, 1920x1080 resolution. DVI, HDMI, CVBS outputs. Built-in 80W LED cold light source. IPX-8 waterproof camera head. USB storage. 11 surgery modes. Video playback function.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Sports Medicine Equipment\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Life Sciences\